      "acceptanceCriteria": "Method of manufactured solutions (MMS) verification must demonstrate observed order of accuracy within 10% of theoretical order for governing equations relevant to blood pump hemolysis prediction.",
      "rationale": "MMS verification performed for incompressible Navier-Stokes with SST k-omega closure. Observed order of accuracy 1.94 (theoretical 2.0), within the 10% tolerance. Benchmark results archived in project verification report VR-2024-003."
