      "rationale": "Three-level Richardson extrapolation study yielded GCI_fine = 1.3% for the hemolysis index at the worst-case operating point (3.5 L/min, 2500 RPM). Asymptotic convergence ratio 1.02 confirms the solution is in the asymptotic range. Achieved level exceeds requirement, providing additional margin."
    },
    {
