      "rationale": "Acceptance criterion of MAE < 0.10 RHI units established in pre-analysis plan PAP-2024-001. Achieved MAE = 0.042 RHI units across 5 operating points. Maximum pointwise error 0.091 RHI units. Both metrics satisfy pre-defined thresholds."
