      "rationale": "The relative hemolysis index (RHI = HI_device / HI_predicate) is the primary regulatory metric for Class II CPB device submissions per FDA guidance. The COU decision criterion RH < 1.0 maps directly to the validation QoI. No surrogate or proxy quantities are used."
    },
    {
