      "rationale": "Validation dataset (Morrison et al. 2017, DOI:10.1115/1.4037267) uses the identical FDA generic pump CAD geometry, 36% glycerol-water blood analog at 37°C, and spans 5 operating points encompassing the COU envelope. Geometric fidelity confirmed by independent CAD comparison. Fluid rheology deviation from whole blood assessed as acceptable at MRL 2."
    },
