      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model selection must be justified by comparison against experimental velocity profiles or hemolysis data; non-Newtonian blood rheology treatment must be documented.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega selected based on literature review of five turbulence models for rotating blood pump flows (Hariharan et al. 2011). Newtonian assumption justified at high-shear CPB operating conditions (shear rates >100 s-1 throughout impeller passage). Model form uncertainty estimated at 12% of hemolysis index variance in UQ campaign, within acceptable range for MRL 2."
    },
    {
