    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 1 for Model Risk Level 2. Validation results demonstrate hemolysis index predictions within pre-defined acceptance thresholds across all 5 COU operating points. The UQ campaign, discussed in the validation reports, confirmed robustness of predictions to dominant input uncertainties. The credibility evidence package is sufficient to support the regulatory decision that the CFD model can reliably identify worst-case hemolysis conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
